Interface NacDayOfWeek.OnWeekChangedListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NacCardHolder
    Enclosing class:
    NacDayOfWeek

    public static interface NacDayOfWeek.OnWeekChangedListener
    Listen for when the day of week is changed. Returning True means that the listener handled the event, and False means that the NacDayOfWeek class will handle the click event, and execute the default action.
